<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="img/willow-&-oak-logo-tab.png">
    <!-- @include 'styles.kit' -->
    <title>Willow & Oak</title>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- @include 'nav.kit' -->
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header__shadow"></div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="header__content">
                <h1 class="header__title heading">rooted in nature, designed for living</h1>
                <p class="header__introduction">At Willow & Oak, we craft warm, sustainable interiors that feel like
                    home.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main class="main">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <section class="about-us section" id="about-us">

                <h2 class="about-us__title heading heading-section">about us</h2>
                <div class="about-us__content">
                    <picture>
                        <source srcset="img/atika-mashal-portait.webp" media="(min-width: 992px)">
                        <img src="img/atika-mashal-portrait-mobile.webp" alt="" class="about-us__img">
                    </picture>

                    <div class="about-us__text">
                        <h3 class="about-us__heading heading">Atika Mashal</h3>
                        <p class="about-us__introduction">Founded by <strong>Atika Mashal</strong>, a designer known
                            for
                            her poetic, grounded approach, Willow & Oak has grown into a collaborative studio where
                            nature meets nuance. Atika’s work is rooted in organic forms, soft minimalism, and
                            timeless
                            palettes that invite stillness and soul.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-us__content">
                    <picture>
                        <source srcset="img/carlos-morandi-portrait.webp" media="(min-width: 992px)">
                        <img src="img/carlos-morandi-portrait-mobile.webp" alt="" class="about-us__img">
                    </picture>
                    <div class="about-us__text">
                        <h3 class="about-us__heading heading">Carlos Morandi</h3>
                        <p class="about-us__introduction">
                            Joining her is <strong>Carlos Morandi</strong>, a detail-driven designer with a love for
                            architectural balance and refined materials. Carlos brings structure and precision,
                            ensuring
                            that every space is as functional as it is graceful.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-us__content">
                    <picture>
                        <source srcset="img/sarah-connors-portrait.webp" media="(min-width: 992px)">
                        <img src="img/sarah-connors-portrait-mobile.webp" alt="" class="about-us__img">
                    </picture>
                    
                    <div class="about-us__text">
                        <h3 class="about-us__heading heading">Sarah Connors</h3>
                        <p class="about-us__introduction"><strong>Sarah Connors</strong> completes the trio with a
                            keen
                            eye for visual storytelling. Her passion for textures, color harmony, and personal
                            touches
                            makes each project deeply intimate and quietly bold.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <section class="our-works section" id="our-works">
                <h2 class="our-works__title heading heading-section">our works</h2>
                <!-- @include 'slider.kit' -->
            </section>
        </div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <section class="how-we-work section" id="how-we-work">
                <h2 class="how-we-work__title heading heading-section">how we work</h2>

                <ol class="how-we-work__steps">
                    <li class="how-we-work__description">
                        <h3 class="how-we-work__step">Discovery & Connection</h3>
                        <p class="how-we-work__text">We begin with a warm conversation to understand your needs,
                            lifestyle, and the feeling you
                            want your space to evoke. This is where we listen, observe, and align with your vision.</p>
                    </li>

                    <li class="how-we-work__description">
                        <h3 class="how-we-work__step">Concept & Moodboarding</h3>
                        <p class="how-we-work__text">Next, we translate your story into a curated concept — a
                            visual direction that blends color, texture, light, and form. You’ll receive a moodboard and
                            design proposal that captures the heart of your project.</p>
                    </li>

                    <li class="how-we-work__description">
                        <h3 class="how-we-work__step">Design Development</h3>
                        <p class="how-we-work__text">With a clear concept in place, we refine layout, materials,
                            and finishes. Every detail — from fixtures to fabrics — is thoughtfully chosen to support
                            both beauty and function.</p>
                    </li>

                    <li class="how-we-work__description">
                        <h3 class="how-we-work__step">Sourcing & Coordination</h3>
                        <p class="how-we-work__text">We handle all the behind-the-scenes: sourcing, ordering, and
                            coordinating with contractors, artisans, and suppliers. Our goal is to make the process
                            seamless and enjoyable for you.</p>
                    </li>

                    <li class="how-we-work__description">
                        <h3 class="how-we-work__step">Styling & Reveal</h3>
                        <p class="how-we-work__text">Once everything is in place, we style your space with
                            intention — adding the finishing touches that make it truly yours. Then comes our favorite
                            moment: seeing you step into your new space for the first time.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>

            </section>
        </div>

        <div class="wrapper">
            <section class="inspirations section" id="inspirations">
                <h2 class="inspirations__title heading heading-section">inspirations</h2>

                <div class="inspirations__grid">
                    <div class="inspirations__grid-item">
                        <img src="img/inspiration-img1.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="inspirations__grid-item">
                        <img src="img/inspiration-img2.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="inspirations__grid-item">
                        <img src="img/inspiration-img3.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="inspirations__grid-item">
                        <img src="img/inspiration-img4.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="inspirations__grid-item">
                        <img src="img/inspiration-img5.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>

        <div class="wrapper">
            <section class="faq section" id="faq">
                <h2 class="faq__title heading heading-section">faq</h2>
                <!-- @include 'accordion.kit' -->
            </section>
        </div>

        <!-- @include 'footer.kit' -->
    </main>
    <!-- @include 'scripts.kit' -->
</body>

</html>